termination_clause.text: TERMINATION.(a) Types of Termination. This Agreement may be terminated:1.By either Party on provision of seven (7) days written notice to the other Party in case of a Force Majeure Event.2.Client has the unilateral right to cancel this agreement at any time within a 7-day notice period. Further, Developer can only canceldue to lack of payment. Client will have a 30 day right to cure before a cancelation can occur.3.By either Party for a material breach of any provision of this Agreement by the other Party, if the other Party’s material breach is notcured within three (3) days of receipt of written notice thereof.
